NK100(the)010:2: 'dod pa'i rtags dang mi 'dod pa'i rtags cha dbye ba'i man ngag go //
NK100(the)010:3: de rnams tshigs sna bsring pa ni gzhung na gsal lo //
NK100(the)010:4: gang zag gi rigs la gnyis te /
NK100(the)010:5: spyi'i rigs chos bcu bzhi dang ldan pa dang /
NK100(the)010:7: de la man ngag gis bzhi ru dbye ste /
NK100(the)010:10: spyod pa'i rigs gti mug gnyen po mtshan bcas dang
NK100(the)010:11: bskyed rims la 'phrod pa'i rigs dang gcig /rgyu'i rigs
NK100(the)010:12: rlung / dbang po'i rigs rnon po /
NK100(the)010:15: rdzogs rims la 'phrod pa'i rigs dang gnyis /
NK100(the)010:19: gnyen po gnyis ka la 'phrod pa'i rigs dang gsum /
NK100(the)010:21: dbang po'i rigs shin tu brtul ba /
NK100(the)010:22: spyod pa'i rigs nga rgyal dang phrag dog shas che ba ni /
NK100(the)010:23: gnyen po sku 'phrod pa'i rigs dang bzhi'o //
NK100(the)010:24: bag chags ngos bzung pa bdun yod kyang bzhi ru bsdu ste /
NK100(the)010:29: sems gnas par bya ba thabs kyi rim pa la gsum ste /
NK100(the)010:30: sems gnas pa'i rgyu bdun 'tshogs par bya ba dang /
NK100(the)010:31: sems gnas su mi ster ba'i nyes pa brgyad spang pa dang /
NK100(the)010:32: de dang mthun pa'i chos brgyad rim pa bzhin ma nor ba rang nyams su blang pa'o //
NK100(the)010:34: rten dang sbyar te 'tshogs la gnas par bya ba dang /
NK100(the)010:35: rigs dang sbyar te rnal 'byor gyi zas bdun gyis khams rtas par bya ba dang /
NK100(the)010:36: dmigs med yul sems gnas pa'i mtshan nyid bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)010:37: spyi rtags nyi shu rtsa bzhis khams kyi tshod bzung ba dang /
NK100(the)010:38: mdo gcod bzhi'i man ngag gis bsgom pa'i thun tshod bzung pa dang /
NK100(the)010:39: nyams dang sbyar te phyir bcos pa'i thabs bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)010:40: bsgom pa rab 'bring gsum lam dgu'i sgo nas sems gnas pa'i tshad bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)010:41: nyes pa drug gam brgyad spang zhing bstan pa'i chos gzhung bzhin bya ba'o //
NK100(the)010:42: sems gnas pa'i mtshan nyid la gnyis te /
NK100(the)010:43: sangs rgyas gsum gyi dgongs pa zung du 'jug pa dang /
NK100(the)010:44: lam drug gi man ngag go //
NK100(the)010:46: ting nge 'dzin shas che ba'i nyams lnga dang /
NK100(the)010:47: shes rab shas che ba'i nyams lnga dang /
NK100(the)010:48: gnyis ka shas che ba'i nyams bdun dang /
NK100(the)010:49: gnyis ka shas chung pa'i nyams bdun dang /
NK100(the)010:50: che chung 'dug pas chung pa che bar byed pa
NK100(the)010:51: la ting nge 'phel ba'i rgyu lnga bsten pa dang
NK100(the)010:52: / shes rab 'phel ba'i rgyu lnga bsten pa'o //
NK100(the)010:53: de gnyis ka 'grib pa'i rkyen lnga spang pa zhon la shes so //
NK100(the)010:54: de ltar 'phel 'grib 'dug pas lam drug bstan de la drug ste /
NK100(the)010:55: dgon drug rten pa'i tshul gyis spyad par bya ba dang /
NK100(the)010:56: mtha' drug spang pa'i tshul gyis spyad par bya ba dang /
NK100(the)010:57: mthun bzhi rten pa'i tshul gyis spyad par bya ba dang /
NK100(the)010:58: mtha' gnyis spang pa'i tshul gyis spyad par bya ba dang /
NK100(the)010:59: kun du bzang po 'phel dang 'grib pa'i tshul gyis spyad par bya ba dang /
NK100(the)010:60: kun du bzang mo 'phel dang 'grib pa'i tshul gyis spyad par bya'o //
NK100(the)010:61: nyams dang sbyar te phyir bcos pa'i thabs la gnyis te /
NK100(the)010:68: thun mong gi nyams bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)010:69: thun mongs ma yin pa'i nyams bac+wa brgyad bstan pa'o //
NK100(the)010:75: bde ba la gnyis thun mong dang /
NK100(the)010:80: mi rtog pa la gnyis te /
NK100(the)010:83: gol sa dang bcad pa la bzhi ste /
NK100(the)010:84: rnam grangs kyi gol sa dgu dang /
NK100(the)010:85: lta ba'i gol sa bcu gnyis las nyi shu rtsa bzhi dang /
NK100(the)010:86: thabs kyi gol sa drug dang /
NK100(the)010:87: mnyam pa nyid kyi gol sgrib sum cu'o //
NK100(the)010:89: bar du gcod pa'i bcu bzhi /
NK100(the)010:90: ting nge 'dzin gyis bsgrub bcu dang /
NK100(the)010:91: ting nge 'dzin gyi skyon drug go //
NK100(the)010:92: man ngag rin chen spungs pa la /
NK100(the)010:93: sprul sku rin po che'i gsung sgros su /
NK100(the)010:95: blo dman don phyir rta yis sdebs /
NK100(the)010:96: 'gro ba 'dren pa'i dpal du shog /khrid kyi lugs kyi 'byed 'grel /
